      "side": 1,
      "message": "For SkSurface, do we want to just assume the mips are allocated but not valid? Or should this be some tri state thing { kNo, kAllocated, kValid }? For image we\u0027d require kNo or kValid, or downgrade kAllocated to kNo.",
